          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="hover-delay" class="doc-h3">Hover Delay</h3>
            <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;">
              <div style="width:48px;height:48px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);border:1px dashed var(--prism-violet);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--prism-violet);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0;">
                <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);">Show: 200ms / Dismiss: 150ms</div>
                <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Add a minimum 200ms show delay to avoid accidental trigger on mouse pass-through. Dismissal can be slightly faster (150ms). On blur (focus loss), use a 300ms delay to allow mouse transfer to the tooltip itself.</div>
